title: Lenovo IdeaPad 510 Review 2017! - Gaming On A Budget?
description:
Hello Guys and Today I'm Going to show You My Review Of The Lenovo IdeaPad 510! This is one of the latest laptops in Lenovo's IdeaPad Series and offers good performance as well as a good build and great display. You can even game on this laptop which is a good thing and is also good for editing and it could be a good laptop if you are a YouTuber as well.

Buy Here: http://amzn.to/2wJVStM

NVIDIA Geforce GTX 940MX Gaming Performance: https://youtu.be/ZAYG0Vc7iP4

Specifications Of The Laptop:
Intel Core i7-7500U
8GB Of RAM
1TB HDD
NVIDIA Geforce GTX 940MX GPU
15.6" Full HD IPS Display

Video Credits: Harsh Punjabi, UrIndianConsumer.

Click Here To Subscribe: https://www.youtube.com/channel/UC0LT37TJKXaTGsAbWIbz_Nw?sub_confirmation=1

Intro Music: Professor Xv - Good Times.
